    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated restoration project or as a comprehensive parts donor. The engine runs very roughly and will require a significant mechanical overhaul to be roadworthy, and the transmission is currently slipping and unreliable. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several dents and faded paint, while the interior requires deep cleaning and repair to the upholstery. Please expect a vehicle that needs substantial work before it can return to the road.",
